Package com.disnodeteam.dogecommander

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Command
    The Command interface is the center of the command-based design pattern.
    Subsystem
    The Subsystem interface represents a physical component of a robot.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DogeBot
    The DogeBot should be inherited by the user; it holds all Subsystems and updates them on their own thread
    DogeCommander
    The DogeCommander does a few things; it runs commands, and it sets when a robot should be updating or not.
